Package hospital

Class Edge

java.lang.Object
hospital.Edge
public class Edge extends Object
The Edge class represents an edge in the graph. It contains the weight of the edge and the rooms it connects. The weight represents the distance between the rooms. The rooms are represented by their id. The edge is bidirectional, so it connects two rooms.
